name: OVERTIME (itch) (VirtualRook)
description:
You have over slept during your shift at the warehouse! You will have to put away the last of the packages in order to get the automatic doors to open, BUT WATCH OUT! Jeff has taken to hunting naughty employees for sport!

Made over the course of 4 months in an effort to learn unreal engine, all 3D assets are mine, sound was found on freesounds.com, most animations are from miximo!

HAVE FUN :D
